  {
   "fieldname": "conditions_help",
   "fieldtype": "HTML",
   "options": "<div class=\"form-message blue\">\n<p><strong>Condition Scripts</strong> are evaluated when the referenced document changes. Use these to control when actions occur:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Assign Condition:</strong> When true, assign users from the table above to the referenced document</li>\n<li><strong>Unassign Condition:</strong> When true, clear all open assignments from the referenced document</li>\n<li><strong>Submit Condition:</strong> When true, auto-submit all reviews this user can submit (e.g., <code>doc.docstatus == 1</code>)</li>\n<li><strong>Validate Condition:</strong> When true, run validation and error if draft reviews exist (e.g., <code>doc.docstatus == 1</code>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Leave blank to disable the action. Scripts have access to <code>doc</code> (the referenced document) and should set <code>result = True</code> or <code>result = False</code>.</p>\n</div>"
